<p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">The HCPC has made </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">six</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> recommendation</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> about the statutory regulation of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">aspirant groups.  They are as follows:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 32pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Psychologists</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">June 2003</span></li><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 32pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="color:#222222; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Clinical Perfusionists</span><span style="color:#222222; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="color:#222222; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="color:#222222; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="color:#222222; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="color:#222